a%20one-stop%20solution%20for%20the%20suggestions%20we%20gave%2C%20and%20we%20eventually%20started%20supplying%20450%20gourmet%20products%20like%20cheese%20and%20other%20perishable%20goods%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Dhanvita.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20venture%20was%20short-lived%20due%20to%20COVID-19%20and%20their%20perishable%20products%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20meet%20its%20consumers%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20demand%2C%20leading%20to%20financial%20losses%20for%20the%20founders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20tangible%20that%20truly%20made%20a%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Srinidhi.%20This%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20Aecoz%20in%202020%2C%20a%20boot-strapped%20startup%20focused%20on%20sustainable%20packaging%20solutions%20for%20the%20food%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPackaging%20out%20of%20paper%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%202019%20plastic%20ban%20may%20not%20have%20achieved%20its%20full%20potential%2C%20it%20served%20as%20a%20valuable%20catalyst%20for%20the%20development%20of%20biodegradable%20packaging%20alternatives%20for%20these%20entrepreneurs.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20%E2%80%98EatFit%E2%80%99%20(a%20food%20outlet%20catering%20to%20your%20diet)%2C%20who%20asked%20for%20biodegradable%20packaging.%20We%20took%20the%20challenge%20seriously%20and%20with%20a%20little%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20were%20successful%20in%20creating%20a%20durable%20yet%20sustainable%20product%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dhanvita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAecoz%E2%80%99s%20paper%20packaging%20production%20begins%20with%20sourcing%20paper%20reels%20from%20ITC%3B%20%E2%80%9CThey%20supply%20about%2085-90%25%20of%20the%20paper%20we%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%2